## Queue Monitoring

```sql
-- Message count by queue
SELECT queue_name, msg_count, newest_msg_age_sec, oldest_msg_age_sec
FROM pgmq.metrics_all();

-- Messages in a specific queue (inspect without consuming)
SELECT msg_id, enqueued_at, read_ct, message
FROM pgmq.q_embeddings_queue
ORDER BY enqueued_at DESC
LIMIT 20;

-- Check archived messages
SELECT msg_id, archived_at, message
FROM pgmq.a_embeddings_queue
ORDER BY archived_at DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

```
Dashboard monitoring:
Dashboard → Integrations → Queues → [queue name]
Shows: message count, read count, oldest message age
Real-time — refresh to see processing progress
```

